infos.info: From Hickerson: The show was also known as - Sunset Serenade 9/6/41-5/30/42 - I Sustain the Wings 5/29/43-6/10/44 - Moonlight Serenade 1940's (syndicated) - Uncle Sam Presents (episodes from 1944) - Command Band 1944 - Mel Powell - Uptown Gang 1944-1945 - AAF Band 1943-1944 - Swing Shift (episodes from 1945) - Propaganda Broadcasts 11/8/1944-12/13/1944 - Glenn Miller Time (episodes from 1961) - In his book, Music Radio, Jim Cox has different dates for the program I Sustain the Wings: 7/10/43-9/4/43 CBS, 9/18/43-6/10/44 NBC.
